Hi HN,<p>Arek here. We’re super excited to officially launch PSPDFKit API [1].<p>PSPDFKit API is a collection of HTTP APIs that enable you to convert, generate, and edit documents without running any service on your infrastructure.<p>What differentiates our API from others is that you can chain together multiple “actions” as part of a single API request. For example, you can convert, OCR, watermark, edit, and flatten a document — all in one call.<p>Available actions [2]:<p>- PDF Generator
- PDF Converter
- Image Converter
- OCR
- Watermark
- Merge
- Split
- Duplicate
- Delete
- Flatten<p>Our documentation includes sample code for JavaScript [3], Python [4], Java [5], C# [6], PHP [7], and the command line. We also have a Postman collection [8].<p>Let us know what you think or if you have any questions.<p>[1] https:&#x2F;&#x2F;pspdfkit.com&#x2F;api&#x2F;
